div.div: Push to a GitHub app repo branch triggers a Cloud Build deployment to scalable serverless Cloud Run platform with Cloud SQL database backend. Developers have also read only access to logs, builds and SQL in Cloud Console. Cloud Scheduler exports the database daily to a Cloud Storage bucket for 3 years. Separated but identical prod, state, etc. environments with infrastructure managed using Terraform configuration automation.
